---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
const title = "Project";
---

<MainLayout title={title}>
  <article class="main-content max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Project</h1>

    <iframe
      src="https://github.com/sponsors/jyoungblood/button"
      title="Sponsor jyoungblood"
      height="32"
      width="114"
      style="border: 0; border-radius: 6px;"
    ></iframe>

    <section id="roadmap" class="mb-12">
      <h2>Roadmap</h2>
      <p>
        Check the <a href="https://trello.com/b/pWMOuOe4/dwjs">Trello board</a> for current development progress.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>0.7.5</strong> - Streamlined existing functionality, everything working and debugged
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>0.8</strong> - GA release with separate npm packages for DW libraries/utilities
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="history" class="mb-12">
      <h2>History</h2>
      <p>
        See the <a href="https://github.com/jyoungblood/darkwave/releases">changelog</a> for release history.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/jyoungblood/darkwave/tree/slime">DW Classic</a> - The legacy PHP-based version.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">
        Darkwave has been in development for over a decade, quietly evolving in the background.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="contributing" class="mb-12">
      <h2>Contributing</h2>
      <p>
        Not accepting contributions at this time. When the project opens up to contributors, the main guideline will be: don't be a dick.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="colofon" class="mb-12">
      <h2>Colofon</h2>
      <p>Thanks to the projects that make this possible:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://starlight.astro.build/">Starlight</a> - Documentation framework
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://fontsource.org/fonts/inter">Inter</a> - Typeface
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://catppuccin.com/">Catppuccin</a> - Code themes
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
